OL,3,CWater bosses warn plans to cap bills
OL,4,Cwill reduce ability to stop sewage
OL,5,Cleaks
OL,7,FITV News Correspondent Sejal KariaI
OL,8,Fexplains why Britain's water companies
OL,9,Fare telling regulators that if they
OL,10,Fcan't put their bills up, their sewage
OL,11,Fleaks will get worse, not better
OL,13,FWater bosses have warned plans to
OL,14,Fintroduce a regulatory cap on bills
OL,15,Fwill hold back firms' ability to stop
OL,16,Fsewage leaks.
