OL,3,CWater bosses warn plans to cap bills
OL,4,Cwill reduce ability to stop sewage
OL,5,Cleaks
OL,7,FIndustry trade association Water UK
OL,8,Fsaid regulator Ofwat's draft plans to
OL,9,Flimit the rise in household water
OL,10,Fbills to #19 a year on average would
OL,11,Fhold back the investment needed to
OL,12,Foverhaul Britain's creaking water
OL,13,Finfrastructure.
OL,15,FThe warnings come just weeks after
OL,16,FOfwat revealed #168 million of
OL,17,Fproposed fines for three of England's
OL,18,Fbiggest water companies for failing to
OL,19,Fmanage sewage spills, including a #104
OL,20,Fmillion penalty for troubled Thames
OL,21,FWater.
