OL,7,FThe company has said it needs to hike
OL,8,Fcustomer bills by up to nearly 60% by
OL,9,F2030 or warned it will become
OL,10,F"uninvestible".
OL,12,FYorkshire Water faced a #47 million
OL,13,Fpenalty while Northumbrian Water faced
OL,14,Fa fine for #17 million after a
OL,15,F"catalogue of failure" in the first
OL,16,Fbatch of results from its biggest ever
OL,17,Finvestigation into the industry.
