OL,3,CWater bosses warn plans to cap bills
OL,4,Cwill reduce ability to stop sewage
OL,5,Cleaks
OL,7,FIn a letter to Ofwat chief executive
OL,8,FDavid Black on Wednesday, Water UK
OL,9,Fboss David Henderson wrote: "Ofwat's
OL,10,Fapproach would make it impossible for
OL,11,Fthe water sector to attract the level
OL,12,Fof investment that it needs and will
OL,13,Freduce the UK's attractiveness to
OL,14,Finternational investment."
OL,16,FOfwat proposed in its draft
OL,17,Fdetermination in July that water firms
OL,18,Fshould be allowed to increase bills by
OL,19,Fa third less than they had requested
OL,20,Fon average.
