OL,4,Cwill reduce ability to stop sewage
OL,5,Cleaks
OL,7,FOfwat said its proposals to cap the
OL,8,Faverage bill increase at 21% ` around
OL,9,F#19 per year ` follows firms'
OL,10,Fproposals to increase their total
OL,11,Fspending by #29 billion, split between
OL,12,Fa #5 billion increase in the core
OL,13,Fcosts for running their business and a
OL,14,F#24 billion rise in spending to meet
OL,15,Frequirements set by governments and
OL,16,Ffor other environmental improvements.
OL,18,FOfwat said at the time that its
OL,19,Fscrutiny of companies' cost proposals,
OL,20,Fto ensure they deliver efficiently,
OL,21,Fhad led to a #16 billion reduction.
